com.kontakt.sdk.android.ble.discovery.eddystone

Interface EddystoneUIDAdvertisingPacket


  • public interface EddystoneUIDAdvertisingPacket
    An interface representing Eddystone UID advertising packet. The packet has the following structure:
    • [0]..[9] - namespace id bytes
    • [10]..[15] - instance id bytes
